entries.journal_entry_description: There's something happening in the Medical Center according to the message from the intercom. This could be another chance to do a good deed.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: Attention all Citizens! The Medical Center is off limits until further notice. There has been a theft. Car'das Agents are on the scene.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Speak with the medical officer and assist with the missing supplies.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Speak with Officer Dreryn in the Medical Center
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to go to the lower level.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Lower Level
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Collect 5 medical supply boxes. The Hutts in the lower levels may have had something to do with it..
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Retrieve Medical Supplies from Storage Room 2
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Use the Elevator to return to the main level.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Main Level
